snippet.title: Clear Vision 2 Flash Game Playthrough
snippet.description:
Clear Vision 2 is the 2nd game in the Clear Vision flash game series.  Jake is back and taking more hit jobs!  Eventually, the feds take notice of his crimes and talent.  They give him no choice but to accept a position in the SD6 to use his skills for good.
